{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NTA5NjUyMTM1", "number": 64117, "title": "Simplify ClusterStateUpdateTask Timeout Handling", "bodyText": "It's confusing and slightly error prone (see #64116) to handle the timeouts\nvia overrides but the priority via a field. This simplifies the code to to avoid future\nissues and save over 100 LOC.\nAlso this fixes a bug in TransportVotingConfigExclusionsAction where trying to instantiate a time value with a negative time could throw and unexpected exception and as a result leak a listener.", "createdAt": "2020-10-25T19:59:05Z", "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/pull/64117", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "ef4ea4ae1030f2ca6dc55e7011bd3397512a32a5"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-10-28T13:26:54Z", "author": {"login": "original-brownbear"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 10, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdWFVI3gH2gAyNTA5NjUyMTM1OjdhNzU5NmMyOTEyMDYwMDkyODhhMzBhOWYxMWNmNGI4NTJkMTQ5YzQ=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdW80l1gFqTUxODYxMTY0Nw==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "7a7596c291206009288a30a9f11cf4b852d149c4", "author": {"user": {"login": "original-brownbear", "name": "Armin Braun"}}, "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/commit/7a7596c291206009288a30a9f11cf4b852d149c4", "committedDate": "2020-10-25T19:56:11Z", "message": "Simplify ClusterStateUpdateTask Timeout Handling\n\nIt's confusing and slightly error prone (see #64116) to handle the timeouts\nvia overrides but the priority via a field. This simplifies the code to to avoid future\nissues and save over 100 LOC."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "a536e26f168b2780a310f432675f5e49ca08530d", "author": {"user": {"login": "original-brownbear", "name": "Armin Braun"}}, "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/commit/a536e26f168b2780a310f432675f5e49ca08530d", "committedDate"